Package Description
squidpony
This is the base package for all components of the SquidLib Library.
squidpony.squidcolor  
squidpony.squidgrid  
The SquidLib Demos are a group of small programs to demonstrate the various ways in which the SquidLib library can be used.

The following demos are currently included:

  • Color Methods Demo: Demonstrates the effects of the available color changing methods.
  • Squid Grid Demo: Demonstrates setting a font arbitrarily in a panel.
